Technical Support

				From classic restorations to modern modifications, the world-famous Holley Technical
				Service team has the answers you need. We provide support for all Holley customers
				with topics including compatibility, applications and suggestions.
			

Instruction Sheets

					Find information about your Holley Brand Product in this easy to use search. 
					Just type in your part number to download.
				
Resource Documents & Library

					Browse our technical documentation and downloads for information like carburetor exploded views and list numbers, NOS nitrous oxide setups, and Holley EFI software and firmware.
				
Frequently Asked Questions

					Be sure and visit our frequently asked questions section for quick answers on carburetor tuning, blower setup, fuel injection setup, intake manifold concerns, and NOS performance.
				
Product Registration

					Fill out your Warranty Registration card online and save postage.
				
Carburetor Warranty

					Lost or misplaced your warranty claim tag?  Click above to print out a replacement warranty claim tag.
				
Holley Brand Warranties

					Holley stands by the name of all of our performance brands.
				
Online Tech Help


					If you have questions about our products, need a part recommendation, or just cant seem to find what you need you can contact our Tech Support online and receive answers by e-mail. 
					Requests may be submitted at any time but please allow up to 48 hours for responses. All questions are answered in the
					order in which they are received. 
					

					Holley Performance Products provides award-winning technical support via phone 
					Monday through Friday from 8AM to 6PM CST, and Saturday from 9AM to 3PM CST @ 270 781-9741. 











